<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Enron_Broadband_trial&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Enron Broadband trial (page does not exist)">Enron Broadband trial</a></li>
<li>The <a href="/wiki/NatWest_Three" title="NatWest Three">NatWest Three</a> - three former UK <a href="/wiki/NatWest" title="NatWest" class="mw-redirect">NatWest</a> bankers, recently <a href="/wiki/Extradition" title="Extradition">extradited</a> to the United States in a case that has generated considerable controversy about <a href="/wiki/United_Kingdom" title="United Kingdom">UK</a>/<a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">US</a> extradition laws.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/The_trial_of_Kenneth_Lay_and_Jeffrey_Skilling" title="The trial of Kenneth Lay and Jeffrey Skilling" class="mw-redirect">Lay and Skilling trial</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Regents_of_the_University_of_California_v._Credit_Suisse_First_Boston_(USA),_Inc.&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Regents of the University of California v. Credit Suisse First Boston (USA), Inc. (page does not exist)">Regents of the University of California v. Credit Suisse First Boston (USA), Inc.</a></i></li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Nigerian_barge_trial&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Nigerian barge trial (page does not exist)">Nigerian barge trial</a></li>
