<li id="cite_note-84"><b><a href="#cite_ref-84" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=10000103&amp;sid=aKHHN.3en36I&amp;refer=us" class="external text" title="http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=10000103&amp;sid=aKHHN.3en36I&amp;refer=us" rel="nofollow">Bloomberg.com: U.S</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-85"><b><a href="#cite_ref-85" title="">^</a></b> Elkind, P. and McLean, B.: "The Smartest Guys in the Room", pages 152-153. Penguin Group, 2004.</li>
<li id="cite_note-86"><b><a href="#cite_ref-86" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://today.reuters.com/news/newsArticle.aspx?type=businessNews&amp;storyID=2006-05-25T180046Z_01_N25441446_RTRUKOC_0_US-ENRON-TRIAL.xml" class="external autonumber" title="http://today.reuters.com/news/newsArticle.aspx?type=businessNews&amp;storyID=2006-05-25T180046Z_01_N25441446_RTRUKOC_0_US-ENRON-TRIAL.xml" rel="nofollow">[1]</a><sup class="noprint Inline-Template"><span title="&#160;since February 2008" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Dead_external_links" title="Wikipedia:Dead external links">dead link</a></i>]</span></sup></li>
<li id="cite_note-87"><b><a href="#cite_ref-87" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFShaheen_PashaJessica_Seid2006">Shaheen Pasha; Jessica Seid (2006-05-25). <a href="http://money.cnn.com/2006/05/25/news/newsmakers/enron_verdict/index.htm" class="external text" title="http://money.cnn.com/2006/05/25/news/newsmakers/enron_verdict/index.htm" rel="nofollow">"Lay and Skilling's day of reckoning: Enron ex-CEO and founder convicted on fraud and conspiracy charges; sentencing slated for September"</a>. CNNMoney.com<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://money.cnn.com/2006/05/25/news/newsmakers/enron_verdict/index.htm" class="external free" title="http://money.cnn.com/2006/05/25/news/newsmakers/enron_verdict/index.htm" rel="nofollow">http://money.cnn.com/2006/05/25/news/newsmakers/enron_verdict/index.htm</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Lay+and+Skilling%27s+day+of+reckoning%3A+Enron+ex-CEO+and+founder+convicted+on+fraud+and+conspiracy+charges%3B+sentencing+slated+for+September&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Shaheen+Pasha&amp;rft.au=Shaheen+Pasha&amp;rft.au=Jessica+Seid&amp;rft.date=2006-05-25&amp;rft.pub=CNNMoney.com&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fmoney.cnn.com%2F2006%2F05%2F25%2Fnews%2Fnewsmakers%2Fenron_verdict%2Findex.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Enron_scandal"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-88"><b><a href="#cite_ref-88" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFJohn_Porretto2007">John Porretto (2007-06-18). <a href="http://www.chron.com/disp/story.mpl/ap/tx/4900110.html" class="external text" title="http://www.chron.com/disp/story.mpl/ap/tx/4900110.html" rel="nofollow">"Ex-Enron broadband head sentenced"</a>. AP<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.chron.com/disp/story.mpl/ap/tx/4900110.html" class="external free" title="http://www.chron.com/disp/story.mpl/ap/tx/4900110.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.chron.com/disp/story.mpl/ap/tx/4900110.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Ex-Enron+broadband+head+sentenced&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=John+Porretto&amp;rft.au=John+Porretto&amp;rft.date=2007-06-18&amp;rft.pub=AP&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chron.com%2Fdisp%2Fstory.mpl%2Fap%2Ftx%2F4900110.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Enron_scandal"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
